---
<Base
  title="Shopify App Stack Cost Auditor — Find & Cut Wasted App Spend (Free 2026)"
  description="Audit your entire Shopify app stack. Select the apps you use, enter costs, and see total monthly spend vs revenue benchmarks. Identify which apps to keep, optimize, or cancel."
  noWebAppSchema={true}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={faqSchema} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={appSchema} />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Tailwind safelist -->
  <div class="hidden bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-950 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 border-green-300 dark:border-green-700 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-950 text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-400 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-950 text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-400 font-semibold ring-2 ring-blue-500 text-xs text-sm"></div>

  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Shopify App Stack Cost Auditor</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 max-w-2xl">
    Check the apps you use, enter your actual costs, and see your total monthly app spend vs revenue benchmarks. Find which categories are costing more than they're worth.
  </p>

  <!-- Revenue input + summary bar -->
  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-8 items-start sm:items-center">
    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
      <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-1">Monthly Revenue ($)</label>
      <input id="revenue" type="number" value="20000" min="0" step="1000"
        class="w-44 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" />
    </div>
    <div id="summaryBar" class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-4 sm:mt-6">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" id="totalCost">$0</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Total/month</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" id="annualCost">$0</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Annual cost</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold" id="pctRevenue">0%</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">% of revenue</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" id="appCount">0</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Apps active</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Health verdict -->
  <div id="verdict" class="hidden rounded-xl p-4 mb-6 border-2 text-sm"></div>

  <!-- App categories -->
  <div class="space-y-6 mb-10" id="categoryList"></div>

  <!-- Add custom app -->
  <div class="border border-dashed border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl p-5 mb-10">
    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">+ Add Custom App</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <input id="customName" type="text" placeholder="App name" maxlength="40"
        class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 w-48" />
      <input id="customCost" type="number" placeholder="$/mo" min="0" step="1"
        class="border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 w-28" />
      <button id="addCustomBtn"
        class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">
        Add App
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="customApps" class="mt-3 space-y-2"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Category breakdown chart (text-based) -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Spend by Category</h2>
    <div id="categoryChart" class="space-y-2"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Benchmark table -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">App Spend Benchmarks by Revenue Stage</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2 font-semibold border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">Revenue Stage</th>
            <th class="text-right px-4 py-2 font-semibold border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">Healthy App % of Revenue</th>
            <th class="text-right px-4 py-2 font-semibold border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">Typical Monthly Budget</th>
            <th class="text-left px-4 py-2 font-semibold border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">Priority Apps</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700">
          {[
            ['< $5K/mo',       '< 5%',   '$0–$250',    'Email, Reviews only'],
            ['$5K–$20K/mo',   '3–5%',   '$150–$1K',   '+ Upsell, basic support'],
            ['$20K–$100K/mo', '2–4%',   '$400–$4K',   '+ Loyalty, analytics, subscriptions'],
            ['$100K–$500K/mo','1–3%',   '$1K–$15K',   'Full stack + custom integrations'],
            ['$500K+/mo',     '< 1.5%', '$5K–$50K',   'Enterprise + negotiated rates'],
          ].map(([stage, pct, budget, priority]) => (
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800">
              <td class="px-4 py-2 font-medium border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">{stage}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-2 text-right border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">{pct}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-2 text-right border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">{budget}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">{priority}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      {faqs.map(({q, a}) => (
        <div class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">{q}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">{a}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-4 mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">How to Audit Your Shopify App Stack</h2>
    <p>Most Shopify stores accumulate apps slowly — one per problem — without ever reviewing the total cost. A store that added an email app at $45/mo, a reviews app at $79/mo, a page builder at $39/mo, a loyalty app at $49/mo, and a helpdesk at $60/mo is spending $272/mo ($3,264/year) before accounting for Shopify plan and processing fees.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Step 1: Pull your current bill.</strong> Shopify Admin → Settings → Billing → Bills. Your most recent invoice itemizes every app charge. This is your source of truth — not what you think you're paying.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Step 2: Score each app.</strong> For every app, ask: (a) Is it actively generating revenue or saving cost? (b) Do I know the specific ROI? (c) Does Shopify's native feature set now cover this? Apps that fail all three are candidates to remove.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Step 3: Target ≤ 2–3% of revenue.</strong> If your total app spend exceeds this threshold, start cutting from the lowest-ROI categories first: redundant page builders, analytics tools you don't check, and loyalty programs for stores under $20K/mo (too early for loyalty economics to work).</p>
    <p><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Step 4: Negotiate or consolidate.</strong> Apps like Growave bundle reviews + loyalty + wishlist into one price. Yotpo bundles reviews + UGC. These consolidations often cost less than the sum of individual apps and reduce integration maintenance.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Cross-links -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pt-6">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">Related calculators:</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/shopify-hidden-fees-audit/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Hidden Fees Audit</a>
      <a href="/shopify-profit-calculator/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Real Profit Calculator</a>
      <a href="/shopify-plan-comparison/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Plan Comparison Calculator</a>
      <a href="/ltv-cac-calculator/" class="text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">LTV:CAC Calculator</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
